<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>
      Welcome to Blueway Trading Company - Subscription Confirmation
    </title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #0073e6;
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 10px;
      }
      .content {
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .message {
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .signature {
        text-align: right;
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-style: italic;
        color: #666;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <title>
          Welcome to Blueway Trading Company - Subscription Confirmation
        </title>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello User,</p>
        <p>
          Thank you for subscribing to Blueway Trading Company! We're excited to
          have you as part of our community. Your subscription is confirmed, and
          you're now on the list to receive the latest updates, news, and
          special offers from us.
        </p>
        <p><strong>Message:</strong></p>
        <div class="message">
          <p>Here's what you can expect as a subscriber:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Regular updates on new product launches.</li>
            <li>Exclusive access to our promotions and discounts.</li>
            <li>
              Informative newsletters about Blueway Trading Company's industry
              and products.
            </li>
            <li>Invitations to our upcoming events and webinars.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            We value your privacy, and your email address will be used
            exclusively for sending you information related to Blueway Trading
            Company. You can unsubscribe at any time by clicking the unsubscribe
            link in the footer of our emails.
          </p>
          <p>
            If you have any questions, suggestions, or need assistance, feel
            free to reach out to our customer support team at
            <a href="[Customer Support Email]">[Customer Support Email]</a> or
            [Customer Support Phone Number]. We're here to help!
          </p>
          <p>
            Once again, welcome to Blueway Trading Company. We look forward to
            providing you with valuable content and staying connected with you.
          </p>
        </div>
        <p class="signature" style="font-size: 14px">
          Best regards,
          <br />
          Blueway Trading Company
          <br />
          [Your Website URL]
          <br />
          [Your Contact Email]
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
